{"word":"συνανίστημι","slug":"συνανίστημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνανίστημι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-στήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make to stand up</i> or <i>rise together</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <i>to assist in restoring</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> with aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>to rise at the same time</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>τινι</el> <i>with</i> one, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}